      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still runs like a dream! It's in great shape and perfect for someone who wants a reliable, stylish car without the brand-new price tag. I've absolutely loved driving this, and I know you will too. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
