    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity during high-lateral G maneuvers. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a driver\u2019s car, the powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and screams to its 8,000 RPM redline. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. A purist-spec machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
