    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been my pride and joy, maintained with an uncompromising eye for detail. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the slightest signs of careful road use, while the interior remains a pristine, smoke-free sanctuary with supple upholstery and fully functional electronics. Mechanically, it is in excellent health; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts with precision, and a full service history documents its consistent care. Recent additions include a fresh set of premium tires and a comprehensive brake service, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. It strikes the perfect balance for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that shows pride of ownership in every corner.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
