      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
