    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual, the drivetrain remains tight with a recently serviced Variable M Differential Lock ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has undergone preventative rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. Suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected of this iconic M-car. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity\u2014including Double VANOS functionality\u2014is robust and driver-ready.",
